      <title>由于担心最佳回报已经结束，中国债券热潮逐渐消退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/china-s-bond-frenzy-fades-amid-worries-best-returns-are-over</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国政府债券连续五个月的强劲上涨势头似乎将于本月结束，因为避险购买热潮受到第二季度债券发行量增加和人民币贬值预期的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/china-s-bond-frenzy-fades-amid-worries-best-returns-are-over</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 00:10:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
